game.name: Molly Traveler Dress Up
game.description:
Learning about the current fashion trends is a hobby of many girls. However, some girls also like to travel from one place to another to seek for something new in their lives. Today you are going to meet with a girl who also loves travelling and today she looks pretty excited to go on her next new adventure that will take place from New York City to Budapest. There are various other locations where she will also stop to have fun. Join Molly Traveler Dress Up game and have fun with the cute girl!

It will be in your hands to make her trip memorable. She needs your help before heading to any location. Put your dressing skills to test to create a perfect outfit for her in this one of the best games for girls! Make sure to stick to her budget before making a purchase for any product. Your successful effort will also help you grab some coins through which you can buy pants, pets, dresses, hair and more. Her favorite boutique is near to her home, so join her when she shops for any clothing items in online dress-up and shopping game. 

Do your best to make her look beautiful! Wearing a nice outfit will give her much needed confidence when she travels all kinds of places and beautiful cities. Try to be as much creative as you are to select between plenty of awesome clothes and awesome accessories in this dressup game! We have many other top girls games to play for free without download. Also give them a try to seek for the best fun and entertainment available online!
